OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry, sunny and chilly start.
OL,6,FCloud bubbling up during the morning
OL,7,Fbut still with sunny intervals. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickening through the afternoon but
OL,9,Flikely remaining dry. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud breaking through the
OL,12,Fevening, with some late sunny spells.
OL,13,FCloud thickening overnight, with a
OL,14,Fchance of isolated light showers.
OL,15,FLight winds continuing. Cold with a
OL,16,Fchance of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
